item.title: How to estimate flows in ungauged catchments?
item.description: Estimating Streamflow in the Ungauged Sub-basins of Arun Catchment Estimated the streamflow, evaporation, and infiltration along the stream channel in an ungagged glacierized catchment with a distributed hydrologic model, and global gridded datasets.
